            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                    We use these trusted services to make GPRA work. Each has their own privacy policy - we've linked them below so you can review them.
                </p>

                <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-500 pl-4">
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                        <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 hover:underline">Stripe</a>
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        Handles all payment processing for subscriptions. We never see your credit card numbers - Stripe keeps them safe and encrypted.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                        <a href="https://posthog.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">PostHog</a>
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        Analytics to help us improve GPRA. We track things like which features you use and where bugs happen.
                        You can opt out anytime in Account Settings.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                        <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 hover:underline">Anthropic (Claude)</a>
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        Powers the AI-powered chord chart autocreation feature. When you upload sheet music or chord charts,
                        we send the images to Claude to analyze and create chord diagrams. You can also bring your own Anthropic API key.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-4">
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                        <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 hover:underline">Google OAuth & AdSense</a>
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        <strong>OAuth:</strong> Optional sign-in method using your Google account.<br>
                        <strong>AdSense:</strong> Shows ads on the free tier to help us keep GPRA free for everyone!
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="border-l-4 border-pink-500 pl-4">
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                        <a href="https://tidal.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 hover:underline">Tidal OAuth</a>
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        Optional sign-in method using your Tidal account. Perfect for musicians who already use Tidal!
                        Note: Tidal doesn't provide email addresses, so we create a placeholder email for you. You can update it via Stripe's Customer Portal.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="border-l-4 border-red-500 pl-4">
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                        <a href="https://www.mailgun.com/legal/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 hover:underline">Mailgun</a>
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        Sends password reset emails and account notifications. That's all - we don't send marketing emails or spam. Ever. Period.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Data Retention -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                <p>
                    <strong>Practice Events:</strong> We keep your practice history for <strong>90 days</strong>, then automatically
                    delete it. You'll get a reminder 7 days before deletion if you haven't downloaded your data. You can export it
                    anytime as CSV or JSON.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>Account Data:</strong> Your items, routines, and chord charts stay safe as long as your account is active.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>Deleted Accounts:</strong> When you delete your account (either scheduled or immediate), we permanently
                    erase all your data. There's no recovery after deletion - it's gone for good.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cookies -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 mb-8" id="cookies">
