            <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                <p>
                    We use a few types of cookies to make GPRA work:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Session Cookies:</strong> Required for login and keeping you logged in. These are "functional cookies"
                    and don't require consent under GDPR.</li>
                    <li><strong>PostHog Analytics Cookies:</strong> Track how you use GPRA to help us improve it. You can opt out
                    anytime in Account Settings.</li>
                    <li><strong>Dark Mode Preference:</strong> Stored in your browser's localStorage so we remember if you prefer dark mode.
                    (Not technically a cookie, but similar!)</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-4">
                    You can manage your cookie preferences using the banner that appears when you first visit GPRA.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

